### Level 9 — Two paths

```
'(\"........................\"
  \"........................\"
  \"........................\"
  \".........####...........\"
  \"........................\"
  \"P......................G\"
  \"##.................######\"
  \"..###..........####.....\"
  \"........................\"
  \".....#####.####.........\"
  \"########################\")
```

High road or low road. Player picks.

### Level 10 — Ambition

```
'(\"...................######G\"
  \".................####....\"
  \"...............####......\"
  \".............####........\"
  \"...........####..........\"
  \".........####............\"
  \".......####..............\"
  \".....####................\"
  \"...####..................\"
